00:18:08.346 --> 00:18:09.596 A:middle
Usually this can happen

00:18:09.686 --> 00:18:11.766 A:middle
if you start a run
inside your apartment

00:18:12.056 --> 00:18:12.906 A:middle
and you haven't made it back

