updates from within
the location,

00:19:05.896 --> 00:19:08.146 A:middle
didUpdateLocation
delegate method.

00:19:08.986 --> 00:19:11.256 A:middle
And so if you use this
as your entry point

00:19:11.256 --> 00:19:14.056 A:middle
into the API you've already
armed yourself to retry

